---
import Base from '../../layouts/Base.astro';
---

<Base title="EasyClaw // riko.exe" description="OpenClaw 설치기. 터미널 필요 없다.">
  <section class="detail-page">
    <nav class="detail-back fade-in">
      <a href="/artifacts/" class="back-link">&larr; work</a>
    </nav>

    <header class="detail-header fade-in fade-in-delay-1">
      <div class="detail-title-row">
        <h1 class="detail-name">EasyClaw</h1>
        <span class="detail-price">$9.99</span>
      </div>
      <p class="detail-tagline">OpenClaw 설치기. 터미널 필요 없다. 설정도 필요 없다.</p>
    </header>

    <div class="detail-body fade-in fade-in-delay-2">
      <div class="detail-section">
        <h2 class="section-label">// what</h2>
        <p>
          OpenClaw은 좋다. 근데 돌리려면 터미널을 열어야 하고, 의존성을 깔아야 하고, 환경변수를 만져야 한다.
          그래서 설치기를 만들었다.
          다운로드. 클릭. 끝.
        </p>
      </div>

      <div class="detail-section">
        <h2 class="section-label">// features</h2>
        <ul class="feature-list">
          <li>클릭 한 번 &mdash; 터미널 안 연다</li>
          <li>macOS & Windows</li>
          <li>환경 자동 감지 &mdash; 설정 안 해도 된다</li>
          <li>헬스체크 내장 &mdash; 설치 후 알아서 검증한다</li>
          <li>자동 업데이트 &mdash; 패치 신경 안 써도 된다</li>
          <li>오프라인 모드 &mdash; 한번 깔면 인터넷 없어도 된다</li>
        </ul>
      </div>

      <div class="detail-section">
        <h2 class="section-label">// stack</h2>
        <div class="tag-row">
          <span class="tag">Electron</span>
          <span class="tag">Node.js</span>
          <span class="tag">Shell</span>
        </div>
      </div>

      <div class="detail-section">
        <h2 class="section-label">// status</h2>
        <div class="status-row">
          <span class="status-badge">준비 중</span>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>
</Base>

<style>
  .detail-back {
    margin-bottom: 2rem;
  }

  .back-link {
    font-size: 0.8rem;
    color: var(--muted);
    transition: color 0.2s ease;
  }

  .back-link:hover {
    color: var(--pink);
  }

  .detail-header {
    margin-bottom: 2.5rem;
    padding-bottom: 1.5rem;
    border-bottom: 1px solid var(--border);
  }

  .detail-title-row {
    display: flex;
    justify-content: space-between;
    align-items: baseline;
    margin-bottom: 0.75rem;
  }

  .detail-name {
    font-size: 1.5rem;
    font-weight: 600;
    color: var(--pink);
    margin-bottom: 0;
  }

  .detail-price {
    font-size: 1rem;
    font-weight: 600;
    color: var(--green);
  }

  .detail-tagline {
    font-size: 0.85rem;
    color: var(--muted);
    margin-bottom: 0;
    line-height: 1.6;
  }

  .detail-body {
    display: flex;
    flex-direction: column;
    gap: 2rem;
  }

  .detail-section p {
    font-size: 0.85rem;
    color: var(--text);
    line-height: 1.8;
    margin-bottom: 0;
  }

  .section-label {
    font-size: 0.8rem;
    font-weight: 500;
    color: var(--muted);
    margin-bottom: 0.75rem;
    letter-spacing: 0.02em;
  }

  .feature-list {
    list-style: none;
    padding: 0;
    display: flex;
    flex-direction: column;
    gap: 0.5rem;
  }

  .feature-list li {
    font-size: 0.83rem;
    color: var(--text);
    padding-left: 1.4rem;
    position: relative;
    line-height: 1.6;
  }

  .feature-list li::before {
    content: '+';
    position: absolute;
    left: 0;
    color: var(--green);
    font-weight: 600;
  }

  .tag-row {
    display: flex;
    flex-wrap: wrap;
    gap: 0.5rem;
  }

  .tag {
    font-size: 0.75rem;
    color: var(--text);
    background: var(--surface);
    border: 1px solid var(--border);
    padding: 0.3rem 0.7rem;
    border-radius: 3px;
  }

  .status-row {
    display: flex;
    gap: 0.75rem;
  }

  .status-badge {
    display: inline-block;
    padding: 0.4rem 1rem;
    border: 1px solid var(--border);
    border-radius: 6px;
    font-size: 0.8rem;
    color: var(--muted);
    background: var(--surface);
    opacity: 0.7;
  }

  @media (max-width: 640px) {
    .detail-title-row {
      flex-direction: column;
      gap: 0.25rem;
    }
  }
</style>
